org.jivesoftware.smack.provider.IQProvider
public class JingleIQProvider
extends Object
implements org.jivesoftware.smack.provider.IQProvider

This class handles the parsing of incoming IQ packets. The provider is registered as explained in the code snippet below in the JingleIQBuddyPacketRouter class

JingleIQProvider jiqProvider = new JingleIQProvider(); ProviderManager.getInstance().addIQProvider(JingleIQPacket.ELEMENT_NAME_JINGLE, JingleIQPacket.NAMESPACE, jiqProvider);
